  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Lost in a realm between worlds, you will fight difficult enemies that traverse harsh lands to recover a mysterious alchemist's reality altering shards. Use your new wind powers to fight your way through hand drawn colorful but dangerous environments to save the worlds.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/cf5836f7dd9f7340d6e4816b17f124b9.avif?t=1774356694\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras_big/cf5836f7dd9f7340d6e4816b17f124b9.avif?t=1774356694 width=800 height=377 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">DANGER IS EVERYWHERE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Danger is everywhere. Everything wants you dead. This is not a path for the faint of heart. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/a88d831c52ac9983ac42b862c618dab2.poster.avif?t=1774356694\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/a88d831c52ac9983ac42b862c618dab2.webm?t=1774356694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/a88d831c52ac9983ac42b862c618dab2.mp4?t=1774356694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">GAIN NEW POWERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You'll gain a plethora of wind powers with unique effects. Upgrade these abilities to become a true force of nature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/dd736f5b739a4372d101f9933f683d6c.poster.avif?t=1774356694\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/dd736f5b739a4372d101f9933f683d6c.webm?t=1774356694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/dd736f5b739a4372d101f9933f683d6c.mp4?t=1774356694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">MORE THAN COMBAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">These powers are more than just ways to fight your enemies. They can also be used to help you traverse through escalatingly difficult worlds. You will leap further, hit harder and fly faster!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/db4e3de75fa6585ecdd4ede824ab872d.poster.avif?t=1774356694\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/db4e3de75fa6585ecdd4ede824ab872d.webm?t=1774356694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/db4e3de75fa6585ecdd4ede824ab872d.mp4?t=1774356694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/fa66b725e41e0176da30931cfc5f7bf3.poster.avif?t=1774356694\" width=640 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/fa66b725e41e0176da30931cfc5f7bf3.webm?t=1774356694\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/fa66b725e41e0176da30931cfc5f7bf3.mp4?t=1774356694\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">SAVE THE WORLDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">An alchemist's mistake has put many worlds in danger. Including yours. Use your new powers to recover his reality altering shards before it's too late.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras/3d4cb7765ba85ed3768c5817421e612e.avif?t=1774356694\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2424500/extras_big/3d4cb7765ba85ed3768c5817421e612e.avif?t=1774356694 width=800 height=282 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
